metadata.name: NotifyService with direct messages when recipient is supposed to be following sender when the message chain is initiated by the recipient with a mention to the sender does notify

sql_query.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."uri" = $1 LIMIT $2
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "mentions" WHERE "mentions"."account_id" = $1 AND "mentions"."status_id" = $2 LIMIT $3
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "account_domain_blocks" WHERE "account_domain_blocks"."account_id" = $1 AND "account_domain_blocks"."domain" = $2 LIMIT $3
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "blocks" WHERE "blocks"."account_id" = $1 AND "blocks"."target_account_id" = $2 LIMIT $3
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "mutes" WHERE "mutes"."account_id" = $1 AND "mutes"."target_account_id" = $2 AND "mutes"."hide_notifications" = $3 LIMIT $4
SELECT "statuses".* FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND "statuses"."id" = $1 ORDER BY "statuses"."id" DESC LIMIT $2
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "follows" WHERE "follows"."account_id" = $1 AND "follows"."target_account_id" = $2 LIMIT $3
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "follow_requests" WHERE "follow_requests"."account_id" = $1 AND "follow_requests"."target_account_id" = $2 LIMIT $3

WITH RECURSIVE ancestors(id, in_reply_to_id, mention_id, path, depth) AS ( SELECT s.id, s.in_reply_to_id, m.id, ARRAY[s.id], 0 FROM statuses s LEFT JOIN mentions m ON m.silent = FALSE AND m.account_id = 111361328875194797 AND m.status_id = s.id WHERE s.id = 111361328875202437 UNION ALL SELECT s.id, s.in_reply_to_id, m.id, st.path || s.id, st.depth + 1 FROM ancestors st JOIN statuses s ON s.id = st.in_reply_to_id LEFT JOIN mentions m ON m.silent = FALSE AND m.account_id = 111361328875194797 AND m.status_id = s.id WHERE st.mention_id IS NULL AND NOT s.id = ANY(path) AND st.depth < 100 ) SELECT COUNT(*) FROM ancestors st JOIN statuses s ON s.id = st.id WHERE st.mention_id IS NOT NULL AND s.visibility = 3
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "conversation_mutes" WHERE "conversation_mutes"."account_id" = $1 AND "conversation_mutes"."conversation_id" = $2 LIMIT $3
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "blocks" WHERE "blocks"."account_id" = $1 AND "blocks"."target_account_id" IN ($2, $3) LIMIT $4
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "mutes" WHERE "mutes"."account_id" = $1 AND "mutes"."target_account_id" IN ($2, $3) AND "mutes"."hide_notifications" = $4 LIMIT $5

SELECT "account_conversations".* FROM "account_conversations" WHERE "account_conversations"."account_id" = $1 AND "account_conversations"."conversation_id" = $2 AND "account_conversations"."participant_account_ids" = $3 LIMIT $4
SELECT "statuses".* FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND "statuses"."id" = $1 ORDER BY "statuses"."id" DESC LIMIT $2
